<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Professional Website</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic styling */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        header {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            z-index: 1;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }
        nav {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        nav a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .video-background {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        .video-background video {
            min-width: 100%;
            min-height: 100%;
            width: auto;
            height: auto;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }
        section {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: #fff;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .login-form {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            max-width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .login-form input {
            display: block;
            margin: 10px auto;
            padding: 8px;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
        }
        .login-form button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        footer {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="video-background">
        <video autoplay loop muted>
            <source src="Elite.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            
        </video>
    </div>
  
    <nav>
        <a href="homep.ejs">หน้าหลัก</a>
        <a href="history.ejs">ประวัติการจอง</a>
        <a href="payment.ejs">เพิ่มบัตรเครดิต</a>
        <a href="showcar.ejs">สินค้า</a>
        <a href="login.ejs" class="login-button">เข้าสู่ระบบ</a>
    </nav>
    

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 My Professional Website. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
